channel.description: How do you make bank booths in Edgeville work?

item.title: Bank Booths
item.dc:creator: @coco_zezima coco zezima
item.description:
@coco_zezima wrote:

Well go to client.java search for makeglobalobject Scroll to the bottom of makeglobalobject and just right or copy the one above and then change the first numbers your x coordnation then next numbers change thoughs number to the y coordnation you want the bank booth to be at. Then next set of numbers is the object so if you wanted a bank booth set the numbers to 2213 thats a bank booth. Next how it says 0 -1 -2 -3 Each one represents the way the object is facing.
If its 0 its facing west if its -1 Its facing north if its -2 its facing east and if its -3 its facing south.
So if i wanted to put a bank booth in edgeville and i wanted it facing west i would put.

makeGlobalObject(3093, 3493, 2213, 0, 10); // bank
